DHOL is a fast music player app with powerful and stylish design.It contains various advanced features which make it totally different and superior from other music players.  It supports almost all type of music files like mp3, wav, ac raw and many other. It allows you to manage all music file easily and quickly. Play music songs easily by songs, playlists, artist and album.
Main Features:
- Download Unlimited Music For free.
- Download latest released songs with their lyrics.
- Radio Garden Service - Through which user can listen to the thousands of live radio stations across the world
- Sleep Timer - user can set any time after which music will automatically stop.
- Play all music and audio files.
- 12 band graphical equalizer with presets.
- Select your own color theme.
- Set Song as a Ringtone directly from app.
- Create and edit your own playlist.
- Play songs from folders.
- Share song on different Social Sites directly from app.
- 6 different Now Playing Themes
- Quick Search for Music Files.
- Shuffle and repeat Music.
- Beautiful User Interface of Audio Player.
- A playlist for recently played songs
- Notification music controls.
- Bass and 3D effects in Sounds
- Headset Controls.
